RequestBody.prompt: A drawing of the Seattle skyline in the style of Van Gogh

data.revised_prompt: Depict an expressive illustration of the Seattle skyline, embodying the unique characteristics of Van Gogh's style. Use bold, dynamic forms, vivid, exaggerated colors, and swirling cloud patterns reminiscent of the Starry Night. The artwork should beautifully represent the majestic grey towers of downtown Seattle, the iconic Space Needle, shimmering waters of Elliott Bay, and the scenic Mount Rainier in the background. Use the preferred medium of Van Gogh, oil on canvas, to capture the essence of the enchanting city.
